eventually to the 15,000 principals.

00:11:02.354 --> 00:11:05.013
And then one would hope
that the principals

00:11:05.037 --> 00:11:07.684
got the letter, received it,
understood it

00:11:07.708 --> 00:11:09.638
and started implementing it.

00:11:09.662 --> 00:11:11.309
It was a little bit ridiculous.

00:11:12.684 --> 00:11:15.145
Now, we knew technology was the answer,

00:11:15.169 --> 00:11:17.310
but we also knew
that most of these schools

00:11:17.334 --> 00:11:19.411
don't have a computer or email.

00:11:20.497 --> 00:11:23.580
However, what the teachers do have
are smartphones.

00:11:23.604 --> 00:11:28.283
